Package: mcmcPainter
Type: Package
Title: MCMC-Based Artistic Line and Dot Painting Generation
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("David", "Hodgson", email = "david.hodgson@charite.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: David Hodgson
Maintainer: David Hodgson <david.hodgson@charite.de>
Description: Generate artistic line and dot paintings using Reversible Jump MCMC algorithms. 
    Creates beautiful artwork from target images through iterative optimization of 
    line and dot parameters. Features automatic image analysis, PNG verification,
    intelligent parameter optimization, and high-performance C++ implementation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/davidhodgson/mcmcPainter
BugReports: https://github.com/davidhodgson/mcmcPainter/issues
